367
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,360
<font color="#FFFF00">Ui!</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">- Fröhliche Weihnachten, Pumuckl.</font>

368
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:07,320
<font color="#FFFF00">Ui!</font>

369
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,520
<font color="#FFFF00">Ja, frohe Weihnachten.</font>

370
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:13,280
<font color="#FFFF00">Du hast ja die Schachtel</font>
